et tabbed_header_widget base_widget"><div class="stat_header_widget"><div class="text_container"><h2>Download <span class="object_title">Universal Base Characters</span></h2></div></div><div class="header_nav"><div class="header_nav_tabs"><a href="https://quaternius.itch.io/universal-base-characters" class="nav_btn return_link">Asset Pack page</a></div></div></div><div class="uploads"><div id="upload_list_5263438" class="upload_list_widget base_widget"><div class="upload"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="button download_btn" data-upload_id="15861669">Download</a><div class="info_column"><div class="upload_name"><strong class="name" title="Universal Base Characters[Standard].zip">Universal Base Characters[Standard].zip</strong> <span class="file_size"><span>122 MB</span></span> <span class="download_platforms"></span></div><div class="upload_date"><abbr title="16 December 2025 @ 12:35 UTC"><span class="icon icon-stopwatch" aria-hidden="true"></span> Dec 16, 2025</abbr></div></div></div></div><div class="trouble_link"><a class="trouble_downloading_btn" href="">Downloads not starting?</a></div></div><section class="download_instructions"><p><strong>Download and install instructions from Quaternius:</strong></p><div class="formatted user_formatted"><p><strong>First-Time Setup for Source Version</strong></p>
<p><em>The first time opening a project is going to be slower, due to the engines having to remake the cache/temp&nbsp;files which are deleted to make the projects lighter, after that it will open as any other project.</em>
</p>
<p><strong>UNREAL ENGINE:</strong>
</p>
<p><em>The kits are developed in an older version of Unreal Engine to let people who are not using the latest version still&nbsp;use the kit. If you use a newer version you need to follow these two steps just&nbsp;the first time you open it.</em><span></span><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE4NjQxNTE2LnBuZw==/original/UIL9au.png" loading="lazy"><br></p>
<p><em>The Unreal Engine models were exported in GLTF because of a known scaling bug when importing rigged FBXs from Blender. It recognizes the units wrong and breaks retargeting in some cases.</em></p>
<p><em>Strongly suggest also using GLTF if you want to re-export.</em></p>
<p><em>To import just drag and drop the .glTF.</em></p></div></section><div class="social_footer"><h3>Share &amp; follow</h3><div class="button_list"><a data-follow_url="https://quaternius.itch.io/-/follow?source=download" data-unfollow_url="https://quaternius.itch.io/-/unfollow?source=download" data-register_action="follow_user" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fquaternius.itch.io%2Funiversal-base-characters%2Fdownload%2FeyJleHBpcmVzIjoxNzc5MjcyMzgwLCJpZCI6MzgyMjI1OX0%253d%252eRDQwp6JNGlI4HSS0iVKxBewV6Ns%253d&amp;intent=follow_user" class="follow_user_btn follow_button_widget button" data-user_id="168522"><span class="on_follow"><span class="icon icon-plus"></span>Follow Quaternius</span><span class="on_unfollow"><span class="icon icon-checkmark"></span>Following Quaternius</span><span class="unfollow_label">Unfollow Quaternius</span></a><a data-register_action="add_to_collection" href="https://quaternius.itch.io/universal-base-characters/add-to-collection?source=download" class="button add_to_collection_btn"><span class="icon icon-plus"></span>Add asset pack to collection</a><span class="share_buttons">or share on<div id="simple_social_buttons_5795043" class="simple_social_buttons_widget base_widget"><a rel="noopener" href="https://bsky.app/intent/compose?text=I%20just%20downloaded%20Universal%20Base%20Characters%20by%20Quaternius%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fquaternius.itch.io%2Funiversal-base-characters" title="Share on Bluesky..." class="bluesky_link" target="_blank"><svg aria-label="Bluesky" width="14" height="14" aria-hidden version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="svgicon icon_bluesky" role="img"><path fill="currentColor" d="M3.468 1.948C5.303 3.325 7.276 6.118 8 7.616c.725-1.498 2.697-4.29 4.532-5.668C13.855.955 16 .186 16 2.632c0 .489-.28 4.105-.444 4.692-.572 2.04-2.653 2.561-4.504 2.246 3.236.551 4.06 2.375 2.281 4.2-3.376 3.464-4.852-.87-5.23-1.98-.07-.204-.103-.3-.103-.218 0-.081-.033.014-.102.218-.379 1.11-1.855 5.444-5.231 1.98-1.778-1.825-.955-